{"tid":846143,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"的士司機遭箍頸扯上車後死亡 被指涉曾拳打死者警員：唔想答","createTime":"2018-10-03T07:51:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T08:01:59.000Z","uid":42250,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"da6e14b3e49c0b1ea4da67b795a081bd0b12971b","tid":846143,"uid":42250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T07:51:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181003/58751232\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181003%2F58751232&d=y20W634u0Ambr8VjUlsI4ZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=d041c9a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181003%2F58751232&h=ea138c6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181003/58751232</a><br />\n的士司機遭箍頸扯上車後死亡 被指涉曾拳打死者警員：唔想答<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181003/large/1538549747_4957.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181003%2Flarge%2F1538549747_4957.jpg&h=09a0fab0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警員馬振康<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20130607/18287998\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20130607%2F18287998&d=y20W634u0Ambr8VjUlsI4ZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=fa1fc30a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20130607%2F18287998&h=e53118d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20130607/18287998</a><br />\n案件速遞：賣鬼仔警藏猴屍罰款<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20130607/large/14066331.jpg[/img\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20130607%2Flarge%2F14066331.jpg%5B%2Fimg&d=y20W634u0Ambr8VjUlsI4ZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=60f8ca23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20130607/large/14066331.jpg[/img</a><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本報年初報道有警員在網上兜售完整嬰屍陰牌，警方後來於該警員寓所，搜出一個裝有瀕危猴子「懶猴屬」標本的玻璃瓶。警員昨承認一項管有瀕危動物標本罪，罰款3,000元。<br />\n辯方求情指服務警隊6年的被告<span style=\"color: red;\">馬振康</span>（28歲），因宗教信仰才管有懶猴屬的標本，非作商業用途，他亦不知受瀕危動物條例監管。事件亦令被告將面對警隊紀律聆訊，可能失去工作。<br />\n警方在1月7日到被告的紅磡住所，搜出一個玻璃瓶，瓶內盛有一件浸在液體、狀似屍體的物品，單位內另有一些護身符及泰國佛像產品。被告指去年底花費約5,000港元，向一泰國男子購入該猴屍，否認買賣「碌葛」。<br />\n案件編號：KCCC1733/13"},{"pid":"d1e18efa3cbcd1e09f412e92b1643aa46ddd01f8","tid":846143,"uid":2223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T07:54:11.000Z","msg":"標題與內文不符"},{"pid":"b44b2c08eaca76e37dd5ebb04ac6e1a481fd269d","tid":846143,"uid":42250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T07:55:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/846147/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/846147/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n未出哂就 post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f98415ada3e627e7711bd61eadc50c7b3bb0474","tid":846143,"uid":130320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T07:56:15.000Z","msg":"標題與內文不符"},{"pid":"6034f8c796f72f4cd4d6e447434919bc358fccbd","tid":846143,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T08:01:59.000Z","msg":"佢個樣都幾嬲打<br />\n好想打鳩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}